<p>I would like to add <code>{}</code> wrappers to single line if condition statements without <code>{}</code> wrappers, using find and replace inside Visual Studio 2015.</p>  <p>Sample if:</p>  <pre><code> if (gender == enumGender.male)                 return "Male Object"; </code></pre>  <p>to</p>  <pre><code> if (gender == enumGender.male)  {                 return "Male Object";  } </code></pre>